1
00:00:07,640 --> 00:00:08,920
‪SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:40,280
‪ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‪QUEEN CHU</i>‪ ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:48,840
Tie Ying commands an elite squad
of covert warfare.

4
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,960
Night raid on Wuyang Pass,

5
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,280
fire on Panying Pass,

6
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,520
and massacre at Qingshi Stronghold.

7
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,800
They've never failed.

8
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,320
I've heard about this squad.

9
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:03,000
They always strike on dark, windy nights,

10
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,560
slaying all who stand in their way.

11
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,040
In that case,

12
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,919
I don't think we're likely to win.

13
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:14,800
Not really.

14
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:19,440
This squad excels at night raids
because they have superb hearing.

15
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:22,440
That's why they can move freely
in the darkness.

16
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,640
There's a way.

17
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,680
We can set traps in the bamboo forest

18
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,280
and catch them off guard.

19
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,760
Then we'll shoot them from the shadows.

20
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:37,040
Then, we might stand a chance.

21
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,360
The whistle is our code.

22
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,320
You can use it

23
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,920
to make our people to set traps for you.

24
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:49,480
During the fight, use it to communicate.

25
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:51,960
Thank you.

26
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,800
Tie Ying is mine.

27
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:19,080
Mere child's play.

28
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:08,320
Jiu, when you kill, you have steady hands.

29
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,800
But now, they shake.

30
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,200
I failed to protect you.

31
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,040
Don't mind.

32
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,680
It matters to me.

33
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:22,960
Before, it was an order.

34
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,200
But now,

35
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,720
it's my duty.

36
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,000
And the future?

37
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,280
In the future…

38
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,240
We'll see.

39
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,400
Whatever happens,

40
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,760
I will protect you.

41
00:05:58,880 --> 00:05:59,720
Tie Ying retreated.

42
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,360
Your father is safe now.

43
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:05,680
Thank you, ma'am.

44
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,280
You helped a lot.

45
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:16,840
To protect me, you suffered heavy losses.

46
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,240
I don't know

47
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,560
how I can repay you.

48
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,760
Since we promised to protect you,

49
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,680
we will keep our word.

50
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,240
Tie Ying retreated.

51
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:32,040
But more troops will be sent from Xiaonan.

52
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:35,400
You'd better leave soon.

53
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,800
Wait.

54
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,560
My father gave this to me.

55
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:46,560
When this is all over
and I'm back in the Capital,

56
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:50,000
you people can ask me for rewards
with this jade pendant.

57
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,840
‪WAR ENDS

58
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,400
All right.

59
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:11,160
What a nice piece of jade.

60
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,520
Come on. Take it.

61
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,800
Eat some of this.

62
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,560
Have you noticed

63
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:43,000
the way she looks at you is a bit strange?

64
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,720
She means no harm.

65
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:47,400
But strange, indeed.

66
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,440
I think Tie Ying has fled back to Xiaonan.

67
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:56,000
Xiao Xun's men will come again.

68
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,360
It's not wise to stay here long.

69
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:58,560
Right.

70
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:00,520
We'll leave soon.

71
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:10,800
Ma'am, in that fight, we had three dead
and seven badly injured.

72
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:13,080
Three traps east were ruined
and need to be reset.

73
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,480
Have our men properly settled.

74
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,480
Yes. I'm on it.

75
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,440
Let's go.

76
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,440
You're about to leave?

77
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:33,320
Don't bother to say goodbye.

78
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:34,559
And you have apologized.

79
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:37,120
But I have one question.

80
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:42,400
What exactly happened
during my father's suppression?

81
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,520
I told you, didn't I?

82
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,520
I doubt it.

83
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,200
I want the truth.

84
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:52,080
This stronghold
is totally my father's style.

85
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:55,520
I don't believe
it was just a misunderstanding.

86
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:59,440
In that case, why did Mu Mianhong

87
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,840
jump off a cliff instead of explaining?

88
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,200
If you don't tell me,

89
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:15,240
I might as well go ask my father.

90
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,480
Do you know your father well?

91
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,080
What kind of man

92
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,120
do you think he is?

93
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,560
My father…

94
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,800
He's the God of War of our state

95
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:45,160
and an all-powerful frontier hero.

96
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,560
People respect him

97
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:49,360
and revere him.

98
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,520
Does that include you?

99
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,560
Do you like this kind of father?

100
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,920
No?

101
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,280
Why?

102
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,880
Because he's a hero to others.

103
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:18,360
He's a hero to people in Yunzhong.

104
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,440
He's a hero to the State of Chu.

105
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:24,960
But I want him to be an ordinary father.

106
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:27,200
Carve wooden dolls for me,

107
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:29,720
watch fireworks with me,

108
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:33,120
give me pretty braids,

109
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:38,280
and be there with me
for every important moment.

110
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,160
But actually…

111
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,320
none of this happened.

112
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,560
What about…

113
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,800
your mother?

114
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:54,400
My mother?

115
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,680
I guess she's a great lady.

116
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,120
According to my father,

117
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:08,040
she's a perfect woman.

118
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:09,880
She was well-learned

119
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:12,480
and versed in all arts.

120
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,720
Sadly, I didn't witness that.

121
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,400
My mother died at a young age.

122
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:26,480
For as long as I can remember,
I have no memories of her.

123
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,200
Sometimes I wish,

124
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,880
if only my mother were alive.

125
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:36,520
Then she would have stood up for me
when Father scolded me.

126
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:39,280
She would do my hair nicely.

127
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:42,560
When people laughed at me
for failing at everything,

128
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,840
she would still treasure me

129
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,680
and always protect me.

130
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:52,400
But what a pity.

131
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:53,760
My mother is gone.

132
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:56,600
Sometimes, I blame myself.

133
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:01,760
Why couldn't I remember everything
when I was born?

134
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:04,000
In that case,

135
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:07,760
I would know what my mother looked like.

136
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:15,360
My father claimed he loved my mother.

137
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,720
But throughout our mansion,

138
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:20,000
in the past 19 years,

139
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:22,560
there has never been
a single portrait of her.

140
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:26,000
In your imagination,

141
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:29,800
what does she look like?

142
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:35,160
She's a noble lady,
according to my father.

143
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:37,960
So she must have

144
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,360
delicate eyebrows,

145
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,760
bright eyes,

146
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,480
and porcelain skin.

147
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,840
Girl,

148
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:58,400
whatever your mother looks like,

149
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,400
your father loves you

150
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,120
more than his own life.

151
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,560
This has never changed.

152
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:21,400
Zhao.

153
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:24,080
How could you not know

154
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:25,600
your letter

155
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:30,680
would make him let down his guard?

156
00:13:31,760 --> 00:13:32,720
You're right.

157
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,400
And that's enough.

158
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,720
Your mother loves you too.

159
00:14:22,920 --> 00:14:25,040
Sorry, I failed.

160
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:26,360
Please forgive me.

161
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:30,680
Where are our men?

162
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,400
The terrain there is eerie.

163
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,560
Too many traps in the forest.

164
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:38,520
We lost over half of our men.

165
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:42,360
But I've figured out their defenses.

166
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,560
I request another attack.

167
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:47,040
Chu Zhao isn't stupid enough
to wait there to die.

168
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:49,480
She's eager to go back to Yunzhong.

169
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:51,400
She won't stay long there.

170
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:55,360
She has to pass through Wangcheng
to get to Yunzhong.

171
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:58,240
Since Cangmu Stronghold
is tough to invade,

172
00:15:00,280 --> 00:15:01,920
we'll be waiting for her further ahead.

173
00:15:02,920 --> 00:15:05,080
Cangmu Stronghold lies at a key junction.

174
00:15:05,160 --> 00:15:06,720
If Chu Ling incorporates them,

175
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,920
he will be more formidable.

176
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:12,960
Tie Ying,

177
00:15:14,040 --> 00:15:15,280
send word to the Northern Desert.

178
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:20,680
Tell them I want another deal
with their king.

179
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:30,040
Congratulations. You won again.

180
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:36,400
Do you think

181
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:40,680
Zhao will be in trouble?

182
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,440
Don't worry. Your Majesty.

183
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:44,520
Before Her Highness left,
I divined for her.

184
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:47,640
During the trip,
she'll escape all misfortune.

185
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,720
Your Majesty.

186
00:15:55,400 --> 00:15:57,600
Uncle, did you come so late

187
00:15:57,680 --> 00:16:00,120
because Zhao and Uncle Yanlai
were in some trouble?

188
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:03,640
Yanlai is skilled in martial arts.

189
00:16:03,720 --> 00:16:05,160
He'll protect Zhao.

190
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,560
Don't worry.

191
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:08,320
General Chu Ling

192
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:10,640
killed the envoy without permission.

193
00:16:11,160 --> 00:16:12,480
It might lead to trouble.

194
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:14,680
His old illness relapsed too.

195
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:16,240
He might not survive this winter.

196
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:20,120
In the court, the Grand Mentor said,

197
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:23,800
if General Chu died, war would break out.

198
00:16:24,400 --> 00:16:26,920
So, our frontier forces
should prepare early.

199
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:28,480
Exactly.

200
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:32,720
The 200,000 frontier troops in Yunzhong
safeguard our state.

201
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:35,200
If Northern Desert foes invade…

202
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:36,200
Yu,

203
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:38,560
do you dare to fight in battle?

204
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,880
I will fight.

205
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,200
We people never fear a battle.

206
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:45,560
Good.

207
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:49,320
Let me ask you one more thing.

208
00:16:49,920 --> 00:16:51,080
If Chu Ling dies,

209
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:55,600
who should command
the 200,000 frontier troops?

210
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:59,360
Uncle Yanlai. He has great martial arts.

211
00:17:06,280 --> 00:17:07,200
Your Majesty,

212
00:17:07,280 --> 00:17:09,319
then get the edict ready.

213
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,599
So we can plan ahead.

214
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:13,920
Wait, Your Majesty.

215
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:20,880
Mr. Xie, you're really impatient.

216
00:17:23,079 --> 00:17:26,560
Your Majesty,
military affairs are of vital importance

217
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:28,280
and need court discussion.

218
00:17:29,120 --> 00:17:31,120
Mr. Xie shouldn't have incited you
in private.

219
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:34,840
Mr. Deng,
are you trying to delay military action?

220
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:36,840
I hold the Imperial Seal.

221
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:39,840
Without the seal on it,
this edict will be invalid.

222
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:43,040
The Three Departments
approve troop deployment.

223
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:47,800
It's time for you to end
this practice of nepotism.

224
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:06,360
‪MILITARY CAMP OF NORTHERN DESERT

225
00:18:14,600 --> 00:18:15,720
Word from Xiao Xun.

226
00:18:15,800 --> 00:18:17,120
Chu Ling is seriously sick.

227
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,320
The Chu court is in chaos.

228
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:21,320
He wants 3,000 elite soldiers of ours

229
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:23,720
to bypass Xiaonan and go to Wangcheng

230
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:26,080
to join the Xiaonan Army
in besieging Yunzhong.

231
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:29,640
Then, we'll split his state.

232
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:33,520
He's the most eager of all.

233
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:36,120
After all these years as a hostage,

234
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:38,920
he still hasn't become patient.

235
00:18:39,520 --> 00:18:41,320
Come on, Chu Ling.

236
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:45,480
We've been fighting for two decades.

237
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:48,720
The state you've guarded with your life

238
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:51,520
corroded from within a long time ago.

239
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:58,880
Their ministers scheme against each other.

240
00:18:58,960 --> 00:18:59,800
KING OF NORTHERN DESERT

241
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:01,240
Even a hostage dares

242
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:05,760
to collude with enemies for invasion.

243
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:15,080
Now, it's our time to take over Yunzhong.

244
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:18,520
But mountain defiles
are perilous in Xiaonan.

245
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:20,120
Supplies can't get through.

246
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:24,000
Wangcheng lies to the rear of Yunzhong.

247
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:27,600
It's weakly guarded.

248
00:19:28,320 --> 00:19:31,720
We'll travel light for a night raid.

249
00:19:31,800 --> 00:19:34,120
Capturing it quickly won't be a problem.

250
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:41,320
Go. Tell Xiao Xun.

251
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:44,680
I will wait for him in Wangcheng.

252
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:52,480
WANGCHENG

253
00:19:57,600 --> 00:20:01,160
Son, we need to think carefully.

254
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:05,120
The Northern Desert King is treacherous.

255
00:20:05,200 --> 00:20:08,280
To work with him is to play with fire.

256
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:11,080
He has probed me for years,

257
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,320
but I've never agreed.

258
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:15,360
If we work with him,
there may be unnecessary trouble.

259
00:20:17,280 --> 00:20:18,760
Can you guarantee

260
00:20:19,800 --> 00:20:22,040
that everything will be under control

261
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:24,360
once his soldiers come in here?

262
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:28,480
Without a perfect plan,

263
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:33,520
we might as well wait.

264
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:36,600
Father, I understand your concern.

265
00:20:37,320 --> 00:20:38,520
But in some cases,

266
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:41,480
patience doesn't solve anything.

267
00:20:42,360 --> 00:20:44,840
I don't want to repeat the same mistakes.

268
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:47,840
Chu Ling is badly ill.

269
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,400
This is the perfect moment.

270
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,320
We'll use our northern foes

271
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:54,800
to support our own cause.

272
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:03,840
I get it.

273
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:06,040
Since you've made up your mind,

274
00:21:07,640 --> 00:21:08,520
go ahead and do it.

275
00:21:10,800 --> 00:21:12,120
Thank you, Father.

276
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:17,760
I should send a few men to escort you.

277
00:21:19,040 --> 00:21:21,080
I've brought too much trouble to you.

278
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:22,600
Many innocent people died.

279
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:25,760
I will keep that in mind.

280
00:21:29,040 --> 00:21:30,160
You helped us at all costs.

281
00:21:30,760 --> 00:21:32,960
Whatever you want, just let me know.

282
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,640
We want nothing from you.

283
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:38,600
We just hope you won't forget us

284
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:41,320
when you're back there
and grant us some rewards.

285
00:21:41,960 --> 00:21:43,040
I will.

286
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,360
That jade piece…

287
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:47,640
Please keep it for me.

288
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:49,520
Sure.

289
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:52,800
Cangmu Forest isn't far from Wangcheng.

290
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:55,320
Xiaonan's killers may pursue you, though.

291
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,600
Every half day, Wangcheng soldiers

292
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,640
patrol the foot of the mountain.

293
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:01,600
Be more careful out there.

294
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,760
Thank you for reminding me.

295
00:22:04,840 --> 00:22:05,880
We know what to do.

296
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:08,000
That's good.

297
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,200
Take care.

298
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:22,240
‪GATEWAY OF CANGMU STRONGHOLD

299
00:22:42,520 --> 00:22:44,880
IN HARMONY WITH YIN AND YANG

300
00:22:47,840 --> 00:22:50,840
You issued the transfer edict, right?

301
00:22:53,920 --> 00:22:56,360
Where did you get this?

302
00:22:56,880 --> 00:23:00,560
Theoretically,
this edict should have left the Capital.

303
00:23:01,280 --> 00:23:04,920
Intercepting an imperial edict
is a grave crime.

304
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:06,640
I did intercept it.

305
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:13,240
What does it mean?

306
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:18,400
It means

307
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:20,880
without my approval,

308
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:23,680
it can't be issued.

309
00:23:23,760 --> 00:23:28,080
Do you think I can't hold you accountable
just because of who you are?

310
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:29,480
You can do that.

311
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:32,040
But I advise you not to do that.

312
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:34,440
If we both lose in the end,

313
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:36,760
our state will be in peril.

314
00:23:36,840 --> 00:23:39,920
Since you know that,
why don't you advise yourself?

315
00:23:40,520 --> 00:23:44,160
You don't fear the peril of the state.
Why would I be scared?

316
00:23:44,760 --> 00:23:47,800
So late at night, you visited
His Majesty and coaxed him.

317
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,840
Why can't I ease his burdens?

318
00:23:49,920 --> 00:23:51,520
Of course, you aren't afraid.

319
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:56,400
But the way you ease burdens
is a clear overreach of your authority.

320
00:23:57,360 --> 00:24:00,880
How dare you issue an edict
without His Majesty's decision?

321
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:03,320
Do you also want

322
00:24:04,160 --> 00:24:05,840
to sit on the throne

323
00:24:06,440 --> 00:24:07,920
to ease His Majesty's burdens?

324
00:24:09,040 --> 00:24:11,480
You overestimate me, Mr. Xie.

325
00:24:12,040 --> 00:24:14,560
His Majesty is aware of all this.

326
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:16,320
As for you…

327
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:19,160
Do you really think
Chu Ling's defeat of an enemy army

328
00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:21,040
will bring peace?

329
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:23,680
Once Chu Ling dies a sudden death,

330
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:26,160
Yunzhong troops will fall into chaos.

331
00:24:26,680 --> 00:24:28,960
Then our state will be in real peril.

332
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,000
Others might not know.

333
00:24:31,080 --> 00:24:32,400
But we both know

334
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:36,440
what the Lord of Xiaonan will do
when Yunzhong is in chaos.

335
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:38,600
What will the Lord of Xiaonan do?

336
00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:42,560
You know it perfectly well, don't you?

337
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:46,760
Back then, you insisted
Xiao Xun return to Xiaonan.

338
00:24:47,360 --> 00:24:48,720
When the hostage left,

339
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:50,640
you should have foreseen this day.

340
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,280
Xie Yanfang!

341
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:56,280
Your duty is merely to enforce edicts.

342
00:24:56,360 --> 00:24:58,480
You have no say in military affairs.

343
00:24:58,560 --> 00:25:00,120
This is a real overreach of authority!

344
00:25:01,760 --> 00:25:06,480
WISDOM AND VIRTUES

345
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:16,440
Here's the Grand Princess Token.

346
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:21,080
I'm exercising the veto power
on behalf of Her Highness.

347
00:25:26,360 --> 00:25:28,280
GRAND PRINCESS TOKEN

348
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:37,520
Madam Ge said,

349
00:25:37,600 --> 00:25:40,200
Wangcheng soldiers patrol at this hour.

350
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:41,600
She's right.

351
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:46,720
So, what exactly is your great plan?

352
00:25:47,360 --> 00:25:48,720
We'll "surrender".

353
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:55,240
Are you saying we'll deliberately
let these patrols catch us

354
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:56,160
and take us to Wangcheng?

355
00:25:56,880 --> 00:26:00,280
So, Mr. Xie, show some mercy in the fight.

356
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:03,360
Who are you?

357
00:26:05,800 --> 00:26:06,840
I don't think

358
00:26:07,840 --> 00:26:09,120
there'll be a fight.

359
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:14,480
<i>It's him.</i>

360
00:26:19,120 --> 00:26:20,360
<i>In my past life,</i>

361
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:23,320
<i>he was a vanguard</i>
<i>under my father's command.</i>

362
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:25,640
<i>But now, he seems to be</i>

363
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:29,280
<i>a foot soldier among Wangcheng troops.</i>

364
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:31,120
Liang Qiang.

365
00:26:35,120 --> 00:26:36,600
How do you know my name?

366
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:39,680
Mr. Xie, you don't allow me
to dispatch new generals.

367
00:26:40,560 --> 00:26:42,320
And you seem to have decent excuses.

368
00:26:43,160 --> 00:26:45,840
Actually, it's just because
they are not loyal to you.

369
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:47,640
Then do you think

370
00:26:48,560 --> 00:26:52,600
you can plant your own men
after you stop me?

371
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:54,840
You don't trust me.

372
00:26:56,280 --> 00:26:58,000
I don't trust you either.

373
00:26:59,040 --> 00:27:00,880
So we should place our trust in Chu Ling.

374
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:04,560
We must believe he will handle
everything before he dies.

375
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:06,560
Chaos won't occur.

376
00:27:07,080 --> 00:27:09,320
Northern Desert foes won't invade.

377
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:14,120
Once our state is in crisis,
we'll be in danger.

378
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:16,200
So will Chu Ling.

379
00:27:17,040 --> 00:27:18,040
If our state falls,

380
00:27:18,120 --> 00:27:20,800
as the Grand Princess,
her daughter will die too.

381
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:25,480
Chu Ling won't let her daughter
fall into danger.

382
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:31,440
Fine.

383
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:36,040
Since the generals can't go to Yunzhong,

384
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:38,080
Mr. Xie,

385
00:27:40,720 --> 00:27:45,240
your private troops must not go there too.

386
00:27:51,600 --> 00:27:54,920
I read the files on your father's
connection to the Third Prince.

387
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:00,080
Who are you?

388
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:03,920
The Third Prince was executed.

389
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,200
His subordinates were demoted.

390
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,440
Your family collapsed.

391
00:28:07,520 --> 00:28:09,560
You became a patrol soldier then.

392
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:12,360
Would you really waste your life
in the middle of nowhere?

393
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:16,480
- Who on earth are you?
- I'm here to help.

394
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:18,800
We're merely bandits

395
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,880
who have fled from Cangmu Stronghold.

396
00:28:21,800 --> 00:28:24,200
You patrolled here and ran into bandits.

397
00:28:24,280 --> 00:28:27,000
If you take us back,
you'll make great merit.

398
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:28,760
We just switched allegiance.

399
00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:30,120
Don't be suspicious.

400
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:35,600
You just need to decide
whether you want that credit.

401
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:39,480
Back in Wangcheng,
if you dare to play tricks,

402
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,040
I'll kill you immediately.

403
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:43,600
Since you accept this merit,

404
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:46,160
we will behave ourselves.

405
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:51,360
CHARTING THE COSMOS

406
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:52,280
Mr. Xie,

407
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:59,120
where is your brother
planning to take the Grand Princess?

408
00:29:03,520 --> 00:29:05,600
My brother has been suspended.

409
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,640
Her Highness is recuperating.

410
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,680
I don't know what you mean.

411
00:29:10,360 --> 00:29:12,080
Then let me remind you.

412
00:29:12,800 --> 00:29:15,400
He who holds the emperor
commands the lords.

413
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:17,120
But he who holds the Grand Princess

414
00:29:17,760 --> 00:29:20,160
only commands Chu Ling.

415
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:22,880
It's a bad bargain.
You know that perfectly well.

416
00:29:22,960 --> 00:29:25,040
Then you should also know.

417
00:29:26,640 --> 00:29:28,480
Chu Zhao must not die.

418
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:31,520
She must stay alive.

419
00:29:31,600 --> 00:29:35,880
Only when she's alive
will the court avoid another rebellion.

420
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:40,320
Then our game can keep going, right?

421
00:29:41,040 --> 00:29:42,400
In that case,

422
00:29:43,080 --> 00:29:45,640
hope your ninth brother
will protect Her Highness well

423
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:49,720
as we all expect him to.

424
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:55,040
Of course.

425
00:29:58,440 --> 00:30:00,560
But you're wrong about one thing.

426
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:04,680
My brother didn't take away
the Grand Princess.

427
00:30:05,280 --> 00:30:08,800
Instead, the Grand Princess
took away my brother.

428
00:30:11,520 --> 00:30:15,400
CHARTING THE COSMOS

429
00:30:16,560 --> 00:30:18,360
Mr. Deng, you're pretty bold.

430
00:30:22,040 --> 00:30:24,960
You removed the coffin
bestowed by Her Highness.

431
00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:28,520
Her Highness withdrew from the court.

432
00:30:28,600 --> 00:30:30,120
Why can't I move this little thing then?

433
00:30:44,360 --> 00:30:45,640
Impressive.

434
00:30:45,720 --> 00:30:46,640
Let me try.

435
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:55,320
Hello, Miss Qi. Hello, Lady Tang.

436
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,560
That totally ruined my mood.

437
00:31:04,360 --> 00:31:05,560
What are you talking about?

438
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:06,680
What did we do?

439
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:09,920
Is it because we didn't bow
to Miss Chu Tang?

440
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:11,920
You should be straightforward.

441
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:14,440
Why do you bother to be so sarcastic?

442
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:16,080
All right.

443
00:31:18,760 --> 00:31:21,600
Lady Tang, let me ask you.

444
00:31:21,680 --> 00:31:25,600
Do you know if your uncle General Chu Ling
fails to defend the frontier,

445
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:27,720
people will suffer?

446
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:33,360
I know.

447
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,600
You speak recklessly

448
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:37,280
because you worry
about our state and people.

449
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,440
This is good.

450
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:41,240
Unmarried ladies like us
should pay more attention

451
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:42,440
to state affairs.

452
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:46,040
Only then will we know about the hardships
of our state and people.

453
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:49,120
However, we must not judge by appearances

454
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:51,280
or take a part for the whole.

455
00:31:51,360 --> 00:31:53,080
We didn't speak recklessly.

456
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:55,040
What we said is the truth.

457
00:31:55,120 --> 00:31:56,760
What is truth? What you see is truth.

458
00:31:56,840 --> 00:31:58,160
Did you see with your own eyes

459
00:31:58,240 --> 00:32:01,320
that my uncle failed
and our foes gained an advantage?

460
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:02,960
Don't try to deny it.

461
00:32:06,080 --> 00:32:07,640
Do you know how big Yunzhong is?

462
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:10,200
Do you know how many soldiers
are involved in a battle?

463
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:13,400
Do you know how many people
from the Northern Desert

464
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:16,760
have come to travel
on the trade routes of our state?

465
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:22,280
When the case is investigated,
my uncle will be convicted or vindicated.

466
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:26,200
But now,
no one can convict him without proof.

467
00:32:28,360 --> 00:32:31,760
Once war breaks out,
situations are volatile and intricate.

468
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:34,800
Even the Emperor's orders
aren't always followed.

469
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:38,840
And you don't even know
what exactly happened in Yunzhong.

470
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:40,280
How can you parrot what others say?

471
00:32:41,280 --> 00:32:42,200
Let's go.

472
00:32:44,360 --> 00:32:45,200
LOTUS PAVILION

473
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:46,320
Come on.

474
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:48,440
Tang.

475
00:32:49,080 --> 00:32:50,120
I…

476
00:32:55,040 --> 00:32:56,280
I'm sorry.

477
00:32:56,360 --> 00:32:58,120
Miss Chu, you seem to be in good spirits.

478
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:01,280
Your family is in turmoil.

479
00:33:01,360 --> 00:33:02,440
But you're in the mood for tea.

480
00:33:03,600 --> 00:33:06,040
If you're here for some fun, get in there.

481
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:07,400
More fun with the storyteller.

482
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:10,040
Tang, how can you be so rude to Mr. Deng?

483
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:12,520
He wanted to watch the fun,

484
00:33:12,600 --> 00:33:14,720
then I recommended the opera house.
How was that rude?

485
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:16,960
Has my entire family
already been convicted

486
00:33:17,040 --> 00:33:18,080
that I can't even speak?

487
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:19,160
You can speak.

488
00:33:19,760 --> 00:33:22,640
Lady Tang, your frankness
is quite admirable.

489
00:33:23,240 --> 00:33:24,880
Even if your uncle ends up guilty,

490
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:26,640
the Grand Princess will stand by you.

491
00:33:28,760 --> 00:33:30,960
You've got a point there,
Mr. Deng. Farewell.

492
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:36,920
Tang, wait for me.

493
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:44,320
Oh no.

494
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:46,600
What was I even saying?

495
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:47,600
Yeah.

496
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:49,280
Scared now, huh?

497
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,760
What happened to all that swagger?

498
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:55,160
Come on. Don't tease me.

499
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:58,120
Just now, I lost my temper.

500
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:00,520
I couldn't remember what I said or did.

501
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,520
Now I've come to my senses.

502
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,600
I'm so terrified.

503
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:13,360
Anyway, what's gone is gone.

504
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:16,920
Even if I said that,
who would dare to do anything?

505
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:19,040
Tang,

506
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:22,679
you've changed.

507
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,600
You never argued with anyone before.

508
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:29,480
Not to mention arguing
for General Chu and Chu Zhao.

509
00:34:34,080 --> 00:34:35,560
Oh, my uncle.

510
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:37,960
Please don't get convicted.

511
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:40,400
And Zhao…

512
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:42,159
Come back early.

513
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:45,159
‪WANGCHENG OUTSKIRTS

514
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:54,199
Before fully recovering,
you exhausted yourself again.

515
00:34:54,719 --> 00:34:55,719
I know what I'm doing.

516
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:00,360
Can we trust this man?

517
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:04,480
Liang Qiang is low-ranking,
but he's a regular soldier.

518
00:35:04,560 --> 00:35:07,000
Xiao Xun's troops
won't provoke or inspect him.

519
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:10,800
In this way,
we'll be able to avoid Xiao Xun's spies.

520
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:14,320
Besides, we're taking a carriage now.

521
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:16,240
No soft cushions or pillows.

522
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:18,960
But at least, we don't need to trek.

523
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:20,960
How nice. Two birds, one stone.

524
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:29,760
WANGCHENG

525
00:35:37,120 --> 00:35:38,040
Get them down.

526
00:36:07,520 --> 00:36:08,560
The ruts are weird.

527
00:36:09,160 --> 00:36:11,040
It seems to be a straw cart
heading for town.

528
00:36:13,240 --> 00:36:14,800
The straw binding is loose.

529
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:17,080
Usually, a loosely bound cart bears

530
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:20,000
no more than three to five hundred jin.

531
00:36:20,080 --> 00:36:22,480
But the ruts are deeper
than half a finger.

532
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:23,960
It carries at least

533
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:26,400
800 jin.

534
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:27,920
There's something else in the cart.

535
00:36:31,600 --> 00:36:32,760
Judging from the ruts,

536
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:36,680
no fewer than ten carts
have entered town today.

537
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:40,920
Someone's taking so much trouble
to do something to this town.

538
00:36:41,520 --> 00:36:43,120
This is a strategic frontier town.

539
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:48,040
If it falls, Yunzhong Prefecture
will be attacked from the front and rear.

540
00:36:49,680 --> 00:36:51,720
Xiao Xun sent his men in disguise.

541
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:54,920
But the gate guards should have inspected

542
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:56,880
either disguised men or hidden weapons.

543
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:58,400
By Article ten of the Frontier Code,

544
00:36:59,040 --> 00:37:02,760
a Military Supply Token will exempt
all goods from inspection.

545
00:37:03,600 --> 00:37:05,840
Given Xiao Xun's status,
getting some tokens

546
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,840
would be quite easy.

547
00:37:09,560 --> 00:37:10,400
Follow me in.

548
00:37:11,560 --> 00:37:12,640
You go back now.

549
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:15,520
Keep up.

550
00:37:21,560 --> 00:37:22,720
Your Highness,

551
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:25,080
3,000 elite troops of Northern Desert
passed Xinggu Pass

552
00:37:25,160 --> 00:37:26,800
and reached Shalang Col,
less than 100 li from Wangcheng.

553
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:30,560
Tell them to go along the official road

554
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:33,720
with the travel permit,
disguised as caravans.

555
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:37,520
- Make sure they're well provisioned.
- Yes.

556
00:37:38,120 --> 00:37:40,000
We won't dispatch troops

557
00:37:41,200 --> 00:37:42,520
until they take Wangcheng.

558
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:47,000
Ge. Ge. Bad news.

559
00:37:48,040 --> 00:37:51,000
Our scout spotted
3,000 soldiers headed for Wangcheng

560
00:37:51,080 --> 00:37:52,840
from the official road northwest
toward Xiaonan,

561
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,400
disguised as caravans.

562
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,960
From Xiaonan?

563
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:59,720
Wangcheng is vital
to the rear of Yunzhong.

564
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:01,600
Once it falls,

565
00:38:01,680 --> 00:38:04,400
Xiao Xun will block supplies
within half a day.

566
00:38:05,240 --> 00:38:09,400
By then, the Yunzhong troops
will be besieged with no supplies.

567
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:12,840
Massive soldiers
will be desperately trapped.

568
00:38:14,560 --> 00:38:15,560
Oh no.

569
00:38:16,080 --> 00:38:17,760
At the rate of traveling,

570
00:38:18,680 --> 00:38:20,680
the two of them are just at Wangcheng.

571
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:23,840
JUSTICE HANGS ON HIGH

572
00:38:23,920 --> 00:38:27,880
General, in Cangmu Forest, I caught
two bandits of Cangmu Stronghold.

573
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:30,520
Bandits have done countless crimes.

574
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:31,640
Execute them now.

575
00:38:33,440 --> 00:38:35,360
General, it's easy for you to kill us.

576
00:38:35,440 --> 00:38:38,080
But I wonder if you can remain so decisive

577
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:40,040
when northern foes break into town.

578
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:48,560
How dare you!

579
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:50,440
How could you spread a fallacy here?

580
00:38:50,520 --> 00:38:53,360
If we were real bandits,
why would we come voluntarily?

581
00:38:54,360 --> 00:38:57,240
As we entered town,
we spotted enemy spies in disguise.

582
00:38:57,840 --> 00:39:00,280
The ruts of straw carts
are abnormally deep.

583
00:39:00,360 --> 00:39:01,360
Weapons must be hidden there.

584
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:04,560
Now, instead of executing me,

585
00:39:04,640 --> 00:39:07,600
you should send men
to close the city gate,

586
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:09,320
search the city, and increase security.

587
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,360
Shut up!

588
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:15,720
How dare a bandit
comment on military affairs,

589
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:18,040
stir up unrest, and shake troop morale?

590
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:20,120
I'll chop your heads off now

591
00:39:20,200 --> 00:39:22,320
and hang them
on the city wall as a warning!

592
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:24,000
Kill them!

593
00:39:37,120 --> 00:39:38,240
Brilliant plan.

594
00:39:38,320 --> 00:39:40,080
Xiao Xun didn't kill you.

595
00:39:40,160 --> 00:39:42,120
But someone on your own side will.

596
00:39:42,200 --> 00:39:43,120
You're wrong.

597
00:39:43,640 --> 00:39:46,960
You've been the only one on my own side.

598
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:50,400
Outrageous. Outrageous!

599
00:39:50,480 --> 00:39:53,040
Seize them immediately and execute them!

600
00:39:53,840 --> 00:39:54,680
Don't you dare!

601
00:40:02,600 --> 00:40:04,720
Zhong Changrong,
deputy of the Guard General,

602
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:06,560
is here to see the Grand Princess!

603
00:40:43,600 --> 00:40:44,440
Hey, girl.

604
00:40:46,680 --> 00:40:47,520
Girl.

605
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:15,920
Hey.

606
00:41:19,240 --> 00:41:20,120
Hey.

607
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:21,920
It's been years.

608
00:41:22,560 --> 00:41:23,800
Don't you recognize me?

609
00:41:27,480 --> 00:41:28,400
Mr. Zhong.

610
00:41:29,040 --> 00:41:30,920
Did anyone bully you?

611
00:41:35,160 --> 00:41:36,000
You…

612
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:38,680
You vile creature! Are you blind?

613
00:41:38,760 --> 00:41:41,640
This is General Chu's daughter,
the Grand Princess.

614
00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:43,520
Just now,

615
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:45,880
who were you going to execute?

616
00:41:48,640 --> 00:41:50,160
Sorry, I misjudged you.

617
00:41:50,240 --> 00:41:51,640
Mercy, Your Highness.

618
00:41:53,640 --> 00:41:54,480
My eyes failed me,

619
00:41:55,080 --> 00:41:56,560
and I offended Your Highness.

620
00:41:56,640 --> 00:41:57,480
Please forgive me.

621
00:41:58,720 --> 00:41:59,720
Not your fault.

622
00:42:00,520 --> 00:42:03,440
Your priority is to close the city gate
and defend deep.

623
00:42:03,520 --> 00:42:05,920
Find out Northern Desert foes and weapons.

624
00:42:07,200 --> 00:42:09,080
I swear to hold the city.

625
00:42:10,480 --> 00:42:13,840
Mr. Zhao,
your official headwear is still yours now.

626
00:42:14,560 --> 00:42:19,000
But if this city falls,
you will lose it and your life.

627
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:22,080
I swear to stand and fall with the city!

628
00:42:22,680 --> 00:42:24,720
Leave us right now. Get to work.

629
00:42:31,440 --> 00:42:33,320
Mr. Zhong, why are you here?

630
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:36,560
Your father was worried about you,

631
00:42:36,640 --> 00:42:38,960
so he sent me here
to get you back to Yunzhong.

632
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:40,760
When I was halfway,

633
00:42:40,840 --> 00:42:42,640
I got this man's message,

634
00:42:42,720 --> 00:42:44,760
saying you would reach Wangcheng.

635
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:46,920
I traveled hundreds of li for nothing

636
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:49,160
and rushed back immediately.

637
00:42:49,240 --> 00:42:50,800
You arrived later than I expected.

638
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:54,040
Zhong, you should work on your speed.

639
00:42:55,160 --> 00:42:56,920
How rude. Nonsense.

640
00:42:58,840 --> 00:43:00,400
Report!

641
00:43:00,480 --> 00:43:01,560
‪THE WAY OF HEAVEN, THE JUSTICE OF ALL

642
00:43:01,640 --> 00:43:03,040
Scouts have spotted

643
00:43:03,120 --> 00:43:05,200
3,000 enemy troops came from the north.

644
00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:07,080
They're within 50 li of this city.
